Package frogger.models.levels

A package of levels for the Frogger Game adhering to the MVC design pattern.

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Level
    The abstract class Level defines common methods and adds common Actors and objects of all Frogger Levels Level1, Level2, Level3, Level4, Level5.
    Level1
    The class Level1 is a level that is played by the user in the Frogger Game.
    Level2
    The class Level2 is a level that is played by the user in the Frogger Game.
    Level3
    The class Level3 is a level that is played by the user in the Frogger Game.
    Level4
    The class Level4 is a level that is played by the user in the Frogger Game.
    Level5
    The class Level5 is a level that is played by the user in the Frogger Game.
    LevelFactory
    LevelFactory is the factory of Level concrete subclasses adhering to a modified Factory design pattern.
    Scoreboard
    The Scoreboard class is a class that generates a 4 digit scoreboard in a Level using Digits.
    World
    The abstract class World defines common essential methods of all Frogger Levels.
